overpowering?  I think not, not gonna go into that, several people already pointed that out, soloing its not much at all, and in a raid all it does is decrease downtime, for everryone. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/usilouettesas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Silouette SaS</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#333333>(4/26/02 3:38:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=191.topic&index=53>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mod Rod 2, a little too powerful?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>     we are needed on a raid, they want us there for this, yet thats not what we do during the fight, during the fight we get to nuke like we all thought we would when we made mages.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
