<br>
You're not being very ambitious at all!<br>
<br>
Generally, when I group with a magician and my regular cleric, we're <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> far</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> more aggressive with our mod rod usage.<br>
<br>
Making and using 3 Mod Rod 2's take roughly 22 seconds. It costs 1200 mana, returns 1980 mana, and requires 400 mana to heal up the damage (CH).<br>
<br>
So, the group has a net gain of 380 mana, over 22 seconds.<br>
<br>
That's 17 mana per second... or <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 103 mana per tick</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> when doing the MR2 gig non-stop.<br>
<br>
<br>
That's a lot, but it's probably not too powerful.<br>
